&lt;p&gt;For more information contact Sharon Green, Education Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email Sharon.green@stockport.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;for an informal chat, to arrange a tour of the hospital or a Skype interview&lt;/p&gt;
